WWW-Scraper-Yahoo360 version 0.01
=================================

Yahoo 360 blog service scraper (http://blog.360.yahoo.com).
Allows to extract information from the Yahoo 360
blog service and manipulate it with Perl code.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Date::Parse
  File::Slurp
  HTTP::Date
  JSON::XS
  WWW::Mechanize

